  "elapsed_s": 1.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was right by the front of the gate, with the fancy sign, that Arbeit Macht Frei.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That infamous saying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody got free to work in Birkenau Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the women orchestra was playing in the corner, in a platform, the most beautiful music.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were numb.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't appreciate the music so much, but it gave a little bit of comfort, that if it's music playing, it can't be so bad.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Killing didn't enter my mind, that there is such a thing, that people, healthy people, should be killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was not much time to think, that within minutes, we were herded in the right and into a bathhouse.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- that was some bath house, with the hanging the water-- you know, the shower heads.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called-- the SS called, is there any barber among you?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
